Localization.Name: Bracewell Boots
Localization.Description: Durable, dependable, and comfortable. The Bracewell are high ankle boots designed to thrive amidst unpredictable weather conditions with a water-resistant finish, high-traction soles, and a toggle-locked top enclosure to help keep out any precipitation.
